<h1>Create a New Portfolio item</h1>


<%= form_with(model: @portfolio_item, local: true) do |form| %>       
<%# code copied from views/blogs/new.html.erb!!!
<%#= form_for(@portfolio_item) do |form| % >                        Tutorial version!!!

Though they are different, Both codes worked in new.html.erb!!! 
